These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: camping, chess, drawing, reading
Pet: snake, bird, chinchilla, pony
1. Hobby:drawing is between Pet:chinchilla and Pet:bird##2
2. Hobby:reading is on the left or right of Pet:chinchilla##3
3. Pet:chinchilla is not to the left of Pet:chinchilla##8
4. Pet:bird != Hobby:drawing##6
5. Hobby:drawing is somewhere to the right of Hobby:camping##5
6. Hobby:camping is on the right of Pet:snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Pet   | snake | chinchilla   | pony  | bird |

