.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
Color: chestnut, blue, emerald, grey
1. Color:grey is not to the left of Color:grey##8
2. Food:grapes is somewhere to the right of Food:zucchini##5
3. Food:grapes == Color:blue##1
4. Food:zucchini is between Food:grapes and Food:tomato##2
5. Food:tomato is somewhere between Food:watermelon and Color:chestnut##7
6. Color:emerald is somewhere to the left of Food:tomato##5
7. Color:chestnut is not to the left of Color:chestnut##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| Color    | emerald      | grey | chestnut | blue |

