2. Hobby:chess is not to the left of Hobby:hiking##8
3. Hobby:puzzles is on the right of Music-Genre:disco##1
4. Music-Genre:rock is not to the right of Hobby:puzzles##8
5. Music-Genre:blues == Hobby:chess##1
6. Music-Genre:blues is on the right of Hobby:puzzles##1
7. Music-Genre:metal is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Hobby         | hiking | card-games | puzzles | chess |

